I = Interface
§§ = Done


Interfaces
==========

D Pin

Input
	-InputAnalog
	-InputDigital
	-I Read

Output	
	§§ -I OutputDigital (off, on, toggle)
			-I OutputAnalog (analog,)
	-I Write

-I Resolution (resolution(bits))

§§ Light (brightness)
	§§ -I Rgb (red, green, blue, color(rgb, hex))
		§§ -I Rgbw (white, color(rgbw, hex))

Display (direction,dimensions, justify, cursor, clear)
	-I CharacterDisplay
		-I SegmentDisplay (struct_SevenSegmentCharacter, privat_input-to-struct, 

§§ Temperature (celsius, fahrenheit, kelvin)

§§ Distance (metre, decimetre, centimetre, millimetre, inch, feet, yard)

Devices
=======

Basic
-----

Button		:: InputDigital
Potentiometer	:: InputAnalog

Led		:: Light, OutputAnalog, Pin
LedRgb		:: Rgb, OutputAnalog, Pin
LedRgbw		:: Rgb, OutputAnalog, Pin

Max72xx		:: SegmentDisplay, SPI, Light

Power
	-Power managment



Protocol
========
	-SPI
	-UART/Serial
	-I2C
